                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1252" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SAWYER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 24.) I was sent for, and took the prisoners to the station-house—while there Eliza pointed to her finger, and said, "I will give you this ring if you will endeavour to impress on the mind of the young man that the ribbon fell from the counter." <hi rend="largeCaps">ELIZA EDWARDS</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18390204-751-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
